  "instructions": "<p>Good hunting for knights from level 500+ to hunt at floor -1. The place is close to the depot and is very attractive for everyone, in addition to giving good xp and a good profit.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Enter the place and start catching 5 monsters at a time, as you get more confident, lure more monsters.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è</strong><strong> Take care:</strong></p>\n<p>- When closing the box put a poison bomb on your foot so the summons don't step on and disturb the box.</p>\n<p>- Be smart with the hellhounds, don't get in front of them because they release very powerful waves, which can kill you in a combo.</p>\n<p>- Many monsters run on the red life here, to avoid this renew the <em>exeta res </em>frequently.</p>\n<p>- Avoid walking diagonally (especially with life in yellow) as you can be paralysed and die in a combo.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üõ°Ô∏è <strong>Equipment</strong></p>\n<p>Bring equipment that protects against ENERGY and LIFE DRAIN. Use energy weapon to kill the Demon Outcasts and switch to physical to kill the other creatures.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>FALCON BATTLE AXE is a great for damage and 12% energy protection. You can use it, combining with the BONE FIDDLE that gives 5% protection against life drain.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Prismatic Ring is a plus to protect against physical attacks. üíç&nbsp;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üêæ <strong>Charms</strong></p>\n<p>If you already have the bestiaries here, I recommend the combination:</p>\n<p><strong>ZAP</strong> on DEMON OUTCAST, <strong>PARRY</strong> on DARK TORTURER, <strong>HOLY</strong> on BLIGHTWALKER, <strong>WOUND</strong> on PLAGUESMITH, <strong>FREEZE</strong> on HELLHOUND and <strong>COURSE</strong> on JUGGERNAUT.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>‚öîÔ∏è <strong>Imbuements</strong></p>\n<p>The imbuements I always use on 2-slot weapons are LIFE and MANA.</p>",
